  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Join an all-party government",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has given a written invitation to all members of Parliament to unite for an all-party government.",
        "It is mentioned in the invitation to come together to implement a national all-party program to create economic and social stability.",
        "In order to fulfill the national responsibility, the 19th Constitutional Amendment and the re-introduction of the Parliamentary Oversight Committee system are intended to build a broad dialogue about the next steps, and the President has also requested that the agreement of the MPs and parties be informed promptly."
      ],
